text: Astro Wheel, Astro Wheels, or AstroWheel may refer to: ==Amusement rides== * Astro Wheel (Chance Rides), a 1967 Ferris wheel * AstroWheel (Great Escape), a 1969 attraction in Queensbury, New York * AstroWheel (Six Flags AstroWorld), a 1968 double Ferris wheel in Houston, Texas ==People== * Astro Wheels, an alias of American astronaut Douglas Harry "Wheels" Wheelock
title: Astro Wheel
